data.description: *** BACK ON THE MARKET WITH IMPROVEMENTS *** FULLY RENOVATED in a corner lot and ready for its new owner! This lovely 3 bedroom, 2 bathrooms home in the city of Ocala could be yours! Plenty of yard space for outdoors fun and entertainment. It has a bonus room that can be used as a bedroom or office. The home features a modern and functional kitchen, beautifully renovated. Renovation includes ALL NEW: Roof, AC, kitchen cabinets, laminate and vinyl flooring throughout, stainless steel appliances, granite countertop, paint (interior and exterior), too many to mention! It has a shed in the backyard for extra storage. The home is located close to shopping, grocery stores and restaurants. Schedule your appointment today and make this home your own! Ask your agent about the Seller's Credit towards Closing Costs and Home Warranty.
